The '''Dnalvec Militia''' was a [[Weequay/Legends|Weequay]] military unit based on [[Dnalvec]].

The Dnalvec Militia fought the [[Houk/Legends|Houks]] during the [[Houk–Weequay conflicts]]. [[Adazian Liebke]] was a veteran of the Militia from this time.

